OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fwindy for a time overnight, with
OL,7,Foccasional blustery showers likely,
OL,8,Fmainly from around midnight onwards.
OL,9,FWinds easing a little through the
OL,10,Fearly hours of Easter Sunday, but
OL,11,Fstaying rather breezy and cloudy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA rather cloudy day, but some
OL,14,Fbrighter or sunny spells are possible.
OL,15,FOccasional blustery showers will
OL,16,Fcontinue, but largely clearing east
OL,17,Faround mid-afternoon. A little cooler
OL,18,Fthan Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
