OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbut cloudy Monday. Staying fine with
OL,7,Fwarm sunshine Tuesday, Very warm
OL,8,FWednesday and staying largely sunny.
OL,9,FChilly starts likely throughout,
OL,10,Fespecially Monday, with a patchy frost.
